{"active_answer": "a 2-ply jute, or a 1-ply that is tightly laid", "active_index": 406, "active_question": "What type of jute rope is recommended for a beginner?", "audit_index": 11, "decision": "edit", "document_sha256": "ae167e55ccf429121af0ac278d1a4537dc483f3b844982a03b4fe2df2ae682a6", "edited_answer": "For a beginner especially, I recommend a 2-ply jute, or a 1-ply that is tightly laid. Loose-lay 1-ply jute is a favorite for the experienced, but it takes finesse.", "edited_question": "What jute construction does Knis recommend for a beginner, and why not loose-lay one-ply jute?", "fact_id": "fact-ca976547430364e279f7", "prior_review": {"decision": "keep", "path": "data/manual_reviews/context_merit_audit_v17/context_merit_audit_v17.jsonl", "sha256": "4d4fbe2ad209ed6cc927099977de7e88cab3cfb6579baa9512004e1b8b4f49bf", "version": 17}, "reason": "The edit makes the recommendation explicitly source-attributed and retains the author's reason that loose-lay one-ply jute requires more finesse.", "reason_code": "add_attribution_and_material_rationale", "review_pass": "secondary_prior_keep_reaudit", "reviewed_at": "2026-07-14", "reviewer": "codex-context-merit-audit-v29", "risk_features": {"answer_tokens": 10, "bare_answer_points": 0, "named_person_trivia_points": 0, "pronoun_count": 0, "question_tokens": 10, "risk_score": 0, "short_question_points": 0}, "schema": "context-merit-audit-v29", "source": "rope365", "source_document": "data/raw/rope365_62f7e527bb35b47d.json", "source_document_file_sha256": "f8cb6186d4dc39154196942243bd295df1521d9263138aa2d7a003944c7dc08d", "source_support": "normalized_extractive", "support_evidence": "For a beginner especially, I recommend a 2-ply jute, or a 1-ply that is tightly laid. Loose-lay 1-ply jute is a favorite for the experienced, but it takes finesse. Do not buy a sportscar when you are still learning how to drive.", "support_evidence_sha256": "512729c104483b4805188b5b3f5f194b3ec3294053ba44cc70e66501a8f41ac3", "url": "https://rope36